{"tid":629260,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"會唔會刻意討好上司/老細","createTime":"2018-04-14T14:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T17:07:10.000Z","uid":160107,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"048a06b837d6816444e54bb1a4c1d6f9c2f8cd8b","tid":629260,"uid":160107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T14:10:33.000Z","msg":"有個前同事同我講<br />\n知女上司個仔好鐘意某個卡通人物<br />\n次次fb有關於隻卡通人物嘅post 都會突登tag佢<br />\n其實呢件事本身冇問題<br />\n但佢係視為討好上司嘅手段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實呢啲野係咪必須要做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得自己好摺<br />\n我連wtsapp都唔想主動搵人打好關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ecdbda0462a001d3718fbb65dec9c5a5066e256","tid":629260,"uid":59283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T14:14:43.000Z","msg":"打份工姐<br />\n搞到自己無哂尊嚴為乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c53a1eaed8e26a8083c9697739750ab0013a2604","tid":629260,"uid":129506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T15:27:06.000Z","msg":"唔同玩法啦，佢哩啲又唔會害到同事，冇問題<br />\n<br />\n你鐘意摺都冇問題，冇話邊人啱邊個錯既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c91258298d52216d56a5428e039e2a498ae15547","tid":629260,"uid":146538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T15:30:07.000Z","msg":"濕碎"},{"pid":"2441488cd41bb2d6e15ca2f6492bfaae8e2aa56f","tid":629260,"uid":89240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T15:35:51.000Z","msg":"以前細過唔會宜加做左幾年野會，做擦鞋仔係升得最快"},{"pid":"8ebbf74c9e05252d8a409ba9deccb040e239c4d4","tid":629260,"uid":123774,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T15:42:45.000Z","msg":"討好都高手段d啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嚮舊老細身邊會服待得好周到<br />\n茶水一定暖咁 唔係討好而係必要做<br />\n所以嚮佢叫之前就做好<br />\n<br />\n佢係某國千億公司總裁 出晒名難服侍<br />\n<br />\n試過幾個SVP co